<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>A SONG OF SALVATION</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdampa hehpihna ka he'i,
 Hehpihna maktak mai chuh ahi;
 Mahleh chunglam apatin leiah,
 * Ei hehpih vanga hungkum ahim? (2)

[V2]
 Ahi, hi kei di'n, kei di'n!
 Ahi, hi kei di'n!
 Van Lalpa A hehpihna tawplo ziek chun,
 Kross ah A thii, kei leh nang hinna'n.

[V3]
 2. A thawkgim leh A thipawt zie,
 Kross a a hung thih zie chuh ka he'i;
 Mahleh khawimun ahim bekah,
 * Kei di'n A thawkna chuh gen ahim? (2)

[V4]
 3. Chung Van chanchin chuh mi'n ei hilh,
 Isu mite'n a muh ding uchu!
 Mahleh Van a mun a um em?
 * Kei ding a guonggalh leh bawl zawh sa'n? (2)
 4. Lalpa ka dawtna ei dawngin,

[V5]
 Nang kawm lo kuo kawmah ka chieh dem?
 Na thagau in ei hilh inla,
 * Kei di'n Hukdampa leh Van um chuh. (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>71</hymn_number>
</song>